Products.ProductName: Womens Hooded Resort Wrap
Products.METATAG_Description: The versatile style and packable design of this sun protective hooded resort wrap for women from UV Skinz makes it the ideal beach cover up for travel.
Products.METATAG_Title: Women's Sun Protection Wrap - UV Protection Shawl
Products.ProductFeatures:
Get stylish sun protection and versatile UV clothing for women to bring with you to all of your favorite travel destinations with this stylish UV protection shawl. This super-soft hooded resort wrap is sure to become one of your most-loved piece of UV protection clothing. It makes a great beach cover up, sun protection wrap or open-front flowing jacket over your favorite casual outfit or dress. A featured shawl collar converts to a convenient hoodie whenever you find yourself in need of additional head and neck protection. This long sleeve wrap is made with certified UPF 50+ sun protection fabric.

 

  • Certified UPF 50+
  • Chlorine and Salt Water Resistant
  • Soft, Lightweight, Breathable Fabric
  • Hooded for Additional Head and Neck Protection
  • Mid-thigh Length Cover-Up
  • Draping Shawl Collar with Purl Stitched Edging
  • Travel Friendly, Packable Design
  • Body Length for Size M is 30 1/2â€ as Measured from Side Neck to Hem
  • Easy Care: Machine Wash, Line Dry
  • Imported
